description: Elysian Gangchon Resort is a popular ski resort for skiers. For the convenience of skiers of all levels, there are various ski trails for beginners, intermediates, and advanced levels. Unlike other ski resorts, the unique valley-shaped ski slopes here are extremely safe, and on the ridge-shaped ski slopes, you can experience the fun of skiing while enjoying the beauty of nature. Jiangcun Resort has 10 ski trails, which are divided into valley-shaped and ridge-shaped. The slope of the valley-shaped ski trail is relatively gentle and suitable for beginners. High level skiers. ChannelPark is a popular playground among Gangchon resorts. It has more than 10 facilities. Whether beginners or advanced enthusiasts, they can experience extremegame and meet the needs of different levels.

description: The Samsung Innovation Museum, located in Suwon, South Korea, was established by Samsung Electronics. It has five floors and covers an area of 10,950 square meters. The entire museum is divided into three parts, namely the "Inventor Era", "Enterprise Innovation Era" and "Creation Era". . The purpose of the museum is to tell the world where the electronics industry came from, as well as the source of inspiration for Samsung to continually create standards that define its products.
